For such a public person I’m actually incredibly private. I post these photos and you probably think I work out and diet all day when the truth is that I’ve been suffering from chronic illness that has robbed me of my lquality of life. I’ve lost 19 pounds since March without trying .  I am only skinny because I can’t tolerate most foods, I don’t have energy to exercise. I’ve been on a total of 74 days of 5 different antibiotics since March.  Beware of medications especially proton pump inhibitors. Prilosec caused Small Bacterial Overgrowth, (food poisoning can also cause it) the antibiotics for that caused a recurring deadly c.diff infection.  If I get quiet and don’t post…don’t worry about me. I’m just focusing on healing.  #siboawareness #c.diff #clostridiumdifficile #overuseofantibiotics will cause you more problems that I don’t wish on anyone and #intermittent #gastroparesis was at the root of it. I had never heard of these conditions until i was diagnosed. And it took a year and eight months to diagnose! Please stay vigilant about your own health care , don’t rely on doctors, do your research.  This C.diff is something tens of millions of people a year die from. Stay safe and healthy.  Much love . 🙏 #gastroparesisawarenessmonth
